Package: fdagwr
Type: Package
Title: Functional Multi-Source Geographically Weighted Regression
Version: 1.0
Date: 2025-06-11
Author: Andrea Enrico Franzoni [aut, cre], Alessandra Menafoglio [aut], Sara Sgobba [aut], Giovanni Lanzano [aut]
Maintainer: Andrea Enrico Franzoni <andreaenrico.franzoni@gmail.com>
Description: The package aims to fit a regression model where both response and covariates are functional elements deriving with unidimensioanl domain. Regression coefficients could eventually vary in space, and eventually vary in different spaces (events and stations).
License: GPL-3
Imports: Rcpp (>= 1.0.12), ggplot2, grid, gridExtra, viridis, patchwork, latex2exp
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppEigen
Depends: R (>= 4.0)
SystemRequirements: C++20, BLAS, LAPACK
Suggests: testthat (>= 3.0.0)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
